Group configuration. Participants are placed at the vertices of a square (FL, FR, BL, BR) with an initial inter-personal distance (IPD) between them of 1, 2 or 4 m.

The experiments were carried out at Brown University in a large hall with a 14 m \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
